description: From the Publisher With 30 seriously challenging dot-to-dots and over 30,000 dots, Ultimate Dot-to-Dot will entertain and engage keen puzzlers for hours on end. Join the dots to reveal intricate and detailed images of animals, objects and scenes. From iconic architecture and Aztec patterns, to ornate ornaments and intricate animals, there's something for everyone. With over 1000 dots, each puzzle is an immersive experience that will help you relax and unwind as you mindfully connect the dots on each page. Different coloured sections within each picture offer more scope for creativity , while enhancing the beauty of the completed image. Although designed for adults , this book is equally perfect for children who love a challenge!
